narratives.question_text:
What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
(Your anonymous response to this question may be viewed by Yale College students, faculty, and advisers to aid in course selection and evaluating teaching.)
comments: This was an excellent course. The immune system is complex, but this course balanced both a comprehensive approach to it while also being flexible to student needs - we all learned a lot!

narratives.question_text:
Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
(Your anonymous response to this question may be viewed by Yale College students, faculty, and advisers to aid in course selection and evaluating teaching.)
comments: I would unequivocally recommend the course. You will learn a lot, while having fun. Additionally Professor Fahmy is a joy to learn from.
